txt.en: 'Many foes still wander throughout Dor Amarth. If you find yourself travelling in these lands, you should defeat any foes you come across.'
Ingold, a soldier of Gondor, has scouted Dor Amarth and found many foes still remain.
You have dealt a mighty blow to all foes in Dor Amarth.
Defeated many foes in Dor Amarth.
A notice is pinned to the board, signed by Ingold:\n\n'Many foes still wander throughout Dor Amarth. A brave adventurer is needed to defeat foes in these lands.'
Ingold has asked you to defeat foes in Dor Amarth.
